  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="margin-top: 50px">GitHub Rank in Dimigo</h2>
      <p>
        학생들의 동기부여를 위해 개발된 페이지로, 디미고를 거쳤거나 재학 중인
        사람들의 깃허브 스타 랭킹을 표시합니다.<br />
        추가 및 삭제 요청은
        <a
          href="https://github.com/junhoyeo/github-rank-in-dimigo/issues/new"
          target="_blank"
          >여기</a
        >에 이슈를 남기거나,
        <a href="https://github.com/junhoyeo" target="_blank">레포 소유자</a
        >에게 연락해 주세요.
      </p>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Rank</th>
            <th>Name</th>
            <th>Stars</th>
            <th>Profile</th>
            <th>Bio</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <% rankedUsers.forEach((user) => { %>
          <tr>
            <td><%= user.rank %></td>
            <td>
              <a href="https://github.com/<%= user.id %>" target="_blank">
                <strong> <%= user.name %> </strong>
              </a>
            </td>
            <td>
              <strong>
                <span>
                  <%= user.stars.toLocaleString() %>
                </span>
                <br />
                <small style="font-size: 12px; color: <%= user.changes > 0 ? "#00873c" : "#eb0f29" %>"
                  ><%= user.changes ? user.changes > 0 ?
                  `(+${user.changes.toLocaleString()})`:`(${user.changes.toLocaleString()})` :'' %></small
                >
              </strong>
            </td>
            <td>
              <img
                src="<%= user.avatarURL.split('?')[0] + '?s=256' %>"
                style="
                  border-radius: 50%;
                  min-width: 84px;
                  height: 84px;
                  border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.3);
                "
              />
            </td>
            <td>
              <div class="row"><%= user.bio %></div>
              <div class="row" style="color: rgb(180, 180, 180)">
                <small
                  ><%= user.publicRepos.toLocaleString() %> public repos, <%= user.followers.toLocaleString() %>
                  followers. Updated at <%= user.updatedAt %></small
                >
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <% }); %>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
